description:
This is the SOLD OUT YUCA - Things I haven't said Early Demo's CD from 2004 containing the singles Day Begins, The Great Escape and more.
There was such a demand from fans who missed out on this CD that the band has pressed a limited amount for sale "Exclusively Here"! Tracks:
  1. Intro
  2. Day Begins
  3. The Great Escape
  4. Fade Away
  5. Have you seen her
  6. Be
  7. Interlude
  8. Holly Rd
  9. Theresa
  10. Blind
  11. Hello
  12. Million Times
Regular Price $10

description:

The Black represents your vehicle window!
The sticker comes pre-masked for easy install.
